oai_dc:dc.dc:title: The Big Scoop on Clubs & Organizations
oai_dc:dc.dc:subject: Clubs; Fraternities & sororities; Events
oai_dc:dc.dc:description: For new students in the First Year Experience program, Christian Brothers University held an event to promote all the clubs, honor societies, and Greek organizations on campus. Ice cream was handed out, hence the name.
